data.name: label9.Text
data.value: If you are ready to rearrange songs press sShuffle button. sShuffler will look after first dot occurence separating text from number. If before that dot will be less than 5 characters it will save whole file name. Otherwise it will save only text after that dot. Source files are not overwritten by sShuffler. Output will be available in the folder made in the same location exe file is stored.

data.name: label7.Text
data.value: You may want to check the list if everyting is correct. If you want to remove one or many songs you can do it by selecting them and clicking DEL key. If one of the songs was not added, scroll the log window for errors.
